OL,3,CWhat is the role of the King on
OL,4,Cresults day?
OL,6,FThe Monarch's job is to ask the leader
OL,7,Fof the largest party in the House of
OL,8,FCommons, now Sir Keir Starmer, if he
OL,9,Fcan command the confidence of the
OL,10,FHouse. In other words, does he have a
OL,11,Fworking majority of MPs with which he
OL,12,Fcan form a stable government?
OL,14,FToday, that means Rishi Sunak will
OL,15,Fmake a farewell speech in Downing
OL,16,FStreet, before travelling to see the
OL,17,FKing as prime minister for one last
OL,18,Ftime to tender his resignation at 11am.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
