OL,3,CWhat is the role of the King on
OL,4,Cresults day?
OL,6,FThe King will then invite Starmer to
OL,7,Fattend Buckingham Palace and ask him
OL,8,Fto form the new government.
OL,10,FHe will arrive at Buckingham Palace
OL,11,Faround midday and just before his
OL,12,Farrival certain executive powers are
OL,13,Fvested in the Monarch - although in
OL,14,Freality they will never be used.
OL,16,FBetween David Cameron and Theresa May,
OL,17,Ffor example, there was only 32 seconds
OL,18,Fbetween one car leaving and the new
OL,19,Fone arriving.
